addr="jms-005P">Forester</fr:link>. I am happy to offer personal assistance via the <fr:link
href="https://lists.sr.ht/~jonsterling/forester-discuss"
type="external">mailing list</fr:link>.</fr:p><fr:p>Many aspects of <fr:link
