type="local"
addr="tfmt-000R">forests</fr:link>, such as <fr:link
href="https://github.com/jonsterling/forest"
type="external">my own</fr:link>. Please be aware that my own <fr:link
href="tfmt-000R.xml"
type="local"
addr="tfmt-000R">forest</fr:link> tends to be using the latest (often unreleased) version of <fr:link
href="jms-005P.xml"
type="local"
addr="jms-005P">Forester</fr:link>, so there may be slight incompatibilities.</fr:p><fr:p>Have fun, and be sure to send me links to your <fr:link
